column1: Daily Weather Observations for Mount Hotham, Victoria for March 2016
Prepared at 13:03 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW3055.201603
Most observations taken from Mount Hotham, pressure taken from Mount Hotham Airport.
Mount Hotham Airport is approximately 500metres lower than Mt Hotham, so care should be taken when using the pressure.
Temperature, humidity, wind and rainfall observations are from Mount Hotham {station 083085}
Pressure observations are from Dinner Plain (Mount Hotham Airport) {station 083055}
